title: Livel 50 Velvet Suit Hangers - Heavy Duty Black Clothes Hangers With Non-Slip Premium Finish - 360 Degree Swivel Hook for Coats, Jackets, and Trousers

Durable and Heavy-Duty: Coated with non-slip velvet fabric, these hangers have a strong and sturdy plastic base, capable of holding a variety of heavier coats and jackets with confidence and ease. Suitable for winter coats and heavy garments.

Big Value Pack for the Whole Family: This pack contains 50 velvet suit hangers, ideal for accommodating a growing wardrobe or serving the entire family. A cost-effective choice for any household. Perfect for seasonal storage and bulk buying.

Elegant and Versatile Storage Solution: The slim design and luxurious velvet finish provide a minimalistic and elegant aesthetic, enhancing your home décor while offering practical storage solutions. Perfect for suits, dresses, coats, pants, and more.
